chunk_content: These data must be managed confidentially to ensure the identities of individuals are protected and to prevent further stigma and discrimination of key populations. How to review for data • Numerator ≥ subtotal of each disaggregation: The total number of adults and children newly quality: enrolled on ART should be greater or equal to the sum of all the age/sex disaggregations and pregnancy/breastfeeding status. • Confirm that TX_CURR ≥ TX_NEW.
